lead_paragraph: The Golden State Warriors needed a big lift from their bench to down the Cleveland Cavaliers 104-89 in the NBA Finals opener in Oakland on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Supporting Cast Help Warriors Take First Blood in Finals Series
